SQL_STMT_U.val: select min( r.re_nummer), max(r.re_nummer),count (distinct r.re_nummer) from rekeningen r inner join clienten c on c.cl_nummer = r.re_nummer and c.cl_relatie_type = 1 inner join clientgroepen g on g.cg_code =c.cl_clientgroep and g.cg_renseigneren>0 inner join rekening_soorten s on s.rs_soort = r.re_soort and s.rs_renseigneren>0 where ( ~1 = 0 OR r.re_nummer >= ~1 ) and ( ~2 = 999999999 OR r.re_nummer <= ~2 ) and r.re_soort between 1 and 2999 and r.re_status between 1 and 8

select D.RELATIENR from ( select rownum "RIJ" , C.RELATIENR from ( select distinct r.re_nummer "RELATIENR" from rekeningen r inner join clienten c on c.cl_nummer =r.re_nummer and c.cl_relatie_type=1 inner join clientgroepen g on g.cg_code =c.cl_clientgroep and g.cg_renseigneren>0 inner join rekening_soorten s on s.rs_soort =r.re_soort and s.rs_renseigneren>0 where ( :1 = 0 OR r.re_nummer >= :1 ) AND ( :2 = 999999999 OR r.re_nummer <= :2 ) and r.re_soort between 1 and 2999 and r.re_status between 1 and 8 order by r.re_nummer ) C ) D where mod (D.RIJ,:3)=0
